		<title>How to Use a Mortgage Calculator</title>
		<link>http://www.quickenloans.com/blog/how-to-use-a-mortgage-calculator</link>
		<comments>http://www.quickenloans.com/blog/how-to-use-a-mortgage-calculator#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2015 20:09:13 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Kevin Graham]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Mortgage Basics]]></category>
